name: Double Tiger Double Prospersity 双虎双丰
description:
This work is inspired by the majestic pose by the tigers at the entrance of Chinatown and the iconic People’s Park complex(珍珠 坊) in Singapore.  The artist is also fascinated by juxtaposition of organic forms of the tigers and the grid-like building. Celebrate the energy of the Year of the Tiger!
